[SPEAKER_01] odlučivati, razbori to,

664
00:40:54,539 --> 00:40:59,260
[SPEAKER_01] razbori to što je prava mjera i što ne.

665
00:40:59,500 --> 00:41:01,559
[SPEAKER_01] A, naravno, pogotovo neko ko je, recimo,

666
00:41:01,559 --> 00:41:03,820
[SPEAKER_01] vlasnik nekog poduzeća,

667
00:41:03,820 --> 00:41:07,139
[SPEAKER_01] pa će znati, ovaj, reći da li treba, evo,

668
00:41:07,139 --> 00:41:09,059
[SPEAKER_01] novac usmjeriti tamo,

669
00:41:09,059 --> 00:41:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili novac treba usmjeriti u nekom drugom smjeru,

670
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] ili, evo, stvarno, ovaj,

671
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] evo, i danas, evo, baš sam u novinama čitala,

672
00:41:18,539 --> 00:41:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] je primjer našeg Baby Lazanje,

673
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] vlada mu je darovala 50.000 evora

674
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] i on je automatski, evo, već odlučio

675
00:41:26,980 --> 00:41:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] da tih 50.000 evora želi darovat

676
00:41:29,559 --> 00:41:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] bolnicama, evo, za djecu.

677
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:35,300
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko je to, recimo, plemeniti jedan čin

678
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] i mogli bi reći njemu sasvim prirodno,

679
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:41,260
[SPEAKER_01] jer on automatski isti dan odlučio,

680
00:41:41,260 --> 00:41:44,139
[SPEAKER_01] a to je u biti vježbanje,

681
00:41:44,139 --> 00:41:46,260
[SPEAKER_01] to je vježbanje korak po korak,

682
00:41:46,260 --> 00:41:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] ne, bi ja rekla,

683
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:49,260
[SPEAKER_01] to je ta jedna mjera,

684
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:51,699
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je meni potrebno,

685
00:41:51,699 --> 00:41:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] što ja želim,

686
00:41:53,039 --> 00:41:54,099
[SPEAKER_01] i opet se vraćamo,

687
00:41:54,099 --> 00:41:55,380
[SPEAKER_01] koje je naše poslanje,

688
00:41:55,380 --> 00:41:59,519
[SPEAKER_01] zašto smo mi na ovome svijetu,

689
00:41:59,519 --> 00:42:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] da li smo mi na ovome svijetu,

690
00:42:01,579 --> 00:42:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] evo, da samo uživamo,

691
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:07,400
[SPEAKER_01] da stvorimo neku manju zajednicu,

692
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:11,260
[SPEAKER_01] ili mi imamo neko veće poslanje

693
00:42:11,260 --> 00:42:12,639
[SPEAKER_01] da sa tom zajednicom,

694
00:42:12,639 --> 00:42:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] s tom obitelji koju stvaramo,

695
00:42:14,539 --> 00:42:16,579
[SPEAKER_01] da djelujemo dalje

696
00:42:16,579 --> 00:42:18,159
[SPEAKER_01] i da to dalje širimo

697
00:42:18,159 --> 00:42:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] kršćanske vrijednosti, evo.

698
00:42:20,179 --> 00:42:20,800
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da.

699
00:42:20,800 --> 00:42:23,800
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da, to je u biti kršćanstva,

700
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:25,239
[SPEAKER_02] zapravo i bogatstvo,

701
00:42:25,239 --> 00:42:28,659
[SPEAKER_02] ako imamo određeni uspjeh,

702
00:42:28,659 --> 00:42:29,280
[SPEAKER_02] dakle,

703
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:32,179
[SPEAKER_02] kršćanska, dakle,

704
00:42:32,179 --> 00:42:33,280
[SPEAKER_02] i etika i socijalni,

705
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:34,780
[SPEAKER_02] i taj socijalna dimenzija kršćanstva

706
00:42:34,780 --> 00:42:35,639
[SPEAKER_02] uvijek govori, naravno,

707
00:42:35,639 --> 00:42:37,679
[SPEAKER_02] potrebno je namiriti vlastite potrebe,

708
00:42:37,679 --> 00:42:39,199
[SPEAKER_02] ali svrha i cilj bogatstva

709
00:42:39,199 --> 00:42:41,199
[SPEAKER_02] je blagoslov drugih,

710
00:42:41,199 --> 00:42:44,199
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, da kada smo mi blagoslovljeni,

711
00:42:44,199 --> 00:42:45,739
[SPEAKER_02] određeni materijalnim dobrima,

712
00:42:45,739 --> 00:42:47,239
[SPEAKER_02] to je zaista kršćanski stav,

713
00:42:47,239 --> 00:42:50,079
[SPEAKER_02] onda to ne držimo grčevito za sebe,

714
00:42:50,079 --> 00:42:52,880
[SPEAKER_02] i ne gradimo zidove

715
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:56,199
[SPEAKER_02] oko svojih hacijenda

716
00:42:56,199 --> 00:42:58,260
[SPEAKER_02] ili ne znam kakvih posjeda,

717
00:42:58,260 --> 00:42:58,860
[SPEAKER_02] dakle,

718
00:42:58,860 --> 00:43:00,239
[SPEAKER_02] kao što je primjerice,

719
00:43:00,239 --> 00:43:02,780
[SPEAKER_02] o to Papa Franju često spominje,

720
00:43:02,780 --> 00:43:04,699
[SPEAKER_02] taj slučaj u Latinskoj Americi,

721
00:43:04,699 --> 00:43:05,840
[SPEAKER_02] gdje se onda,

722
00:43:06,119 --> 00:43:08,500
[SPEAKER_02] imamo izrazito jako bogate ljude,

723
00:43:08,500 --> 00:43:11,619
[SPEAKER_02] koji grade te svoje velike posjede,

724
00:43:11,619 --> 00:43:13,539
[SPEAKER_02] koji su maksimalno osigurani,

725
00:43:13,539 --> 00:43:15,500
[SPEAKER_02] i onda nedaleko od takvih

726
00:43:15,500 --> 00:43:17,699
[SPEAKER_02] neslučajnih razmjera bogatstva,

727
00:43:17,699 --> 00:43:19,679
[SPEAKER_02] imamo ljude koji žive u velikoj bjedi,

728
00:43:19,679 --> 00:43:20,320
[SPEAKER_02] ne u velikoj,

729
00:43:20,320 --> 00:43:21,780
[SPEAKER_02] nego u nezamislivoj bjedi.

730
00:43:22,659 --> 00:43:24,039
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, svrha i cilj bogatstva

731
00:43:24,039 --> 00:43:25,699
[SPEAKER_02] nije to ozgrtati ga za sebe

732
00:43:25,699 --> 00:43:27,019
[SPEAKER_02] i čuvati grčevito,

733
00:43:27,019 --> 00:43:29,360
[SPEAKER_02] nego je svrha i cilj bogatstva

734
00:43:29,360 --> 00:43:30,980
[SPEAKER_02] u krčanskoj perspektivi

735
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:33,920
[SPEAKER_02] blagoslov drugih.

736
00:43:34,639 --> 00:43:36,019
[SPEAKER_02] kao što je ovaj primjer

737
00:43:36,019 --> 00:43:36,900
[SPEAKER_02] koji si navjela,

738
00:43:36,900 --> 00:43:38,260
[SPEAKER_02] jer to je,

739
00:43:38,260 --> 00:43:40,199
[SPEAKER_02] ako gledamo Evanđelja,

740
00:43:40,199 --> 00:43:41,880
[SPEAKER_02] Isus Hristo konstantno kaže

741
00:43:41,880 --> 00:43:47,980
[SPEAKER_02] da ne možemo služiti dvojci gospodara,

742
00:43:47,980 --> 00:43:49,679
[SPEAKER_02] ne možemo služiti Bogu i novcu.

743
00:43:49,679 --> 00:43:51,840
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, novac je taj koji

744
00:43:51,840 --> 00:43:54,400
[SPEAKER_02] nije naš gospodar

745
00:43:54,400 --> 00:43:58,239
[SPEAKER_02] u smislu da on čovjekov život usmjeruje,

746
00:43:58,239 --> 00:44:00,500
[SPEAKER_02] nego je čovjek taj koji usmjeruje novac.

747
00:44:00,500 --> 00:44:04,460
[SPEAKER_02] I zato Isus Hristo ima jako lijepih citata

748
00:44:04,460 --> 00:44:07,219
[SPEAKER_02] iz Evanđelja koji se sučava

749
00:44:07,219 --> 00:44:09,539
[SPEAKER_02] i sa vrlo konkretnom ekonomskom tematikom.

750
00:44:09,539 --> 00:44:12,000
[SPEAKER_02] To je bilo zanimljivo isto proučavati,

751
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:14,519
[SPEAKER_02] gdje dobivamo jasne smjernice

752
00:44:14,519 --> 00:44:16,119
[SPEAKER_02] u odnosu prema bogatstvu,

753
00:44:16,119 --> 00:44:18,159
[SPEAKER_02] prema novcu i odgovor na pitanje

754
00:44:18,159 --> 00:44:19,900
[SPEAKER_02] zapravo što je pravo bogatstvo.

755
00:44:19,900 --> 00:44:22,099
[SPEAKER_02] Da li je pravo bogatstvo imati puno novaca?

756
00:44:22,099 --> 00:44:26,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ili je bogatstvo negdje drugdje?

757
00:44:26,960 --> 00:44:29,340
[SPEAKER_02] Papa Franjo također kaže

758
00:44:29,340 --> 00:44:30,920
[SPEAKER_02] da je neki od naj...

759
00:44:30,920 --> 00:44:33,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ako bogatstvo često vezujemo

760
00:44:33,039 --> 00:44:34,000
[SPEAKER_02] uz koncept sreće,

761
00:44:34,079 --> 00:44:35,639
[SPEAKER_02] bit ćemo sretnije ako smo bogati.

762
00:44:35,639 --> 00:44:36,960
[SPEAKER_02] A Papa Franjo kaže

763
00:44:36,960 --> 00:44:42,139
[SPEAKER_02] ne, ja sam najskrenije iskustva sreće

764
00:44:42,139 --> 00:44:44,639
[SPEAKER_02] vidio na licima najsiromašnijih ljudi.

765
00:44:44,639 --> 00:44:48,199
[SPEAKER_02] I sad kaže on to u Apostolskoj pobodnici

766
00:44:48,199 --> 00:44:49,119
[SPEAKER_02] Evangelii Gaudium,

767
00:44:49,119 --> 00:44:50,059
[SPEAKER_02] radost evanđelja.

768
00:44:50,059 --> 00:44:51,440
[SPEAKER_02] I naravno sad se možemo zapitati

769
00:44:51,440 --> 00:44:52,199
[SPEAKER_02] kako, kako?

770
00:44:52,199 --> 00:44:53,659
[SPEAKER_02] Kod najsiromašnijih.

771
00:44:53,659 --> 00:44:55,719
[SPEAKER_02] A on kaže zato jer se oni nemaju

772
00:44:55,719 --> 00:44:56,880
[SPEAKER_02] na što navezati.

773
00:44:56,880 --> 00:44:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, to je nema ih što vezati,

774
00:44:59,559 --> 00:45:00,699
[SPEAKER_02] a s druge strane

775
00:45:00,699 --> 00:45:02,360
[SPEAKER_02] onda imaju jedni druge

776
00:45:02,360 --> 00:45:03,619
[SPEAKER_02] kao najveće bogatstvo.

777
00:45:03,699 --> 00:45:05,039
[SPEAKER_01] Imaju jedne druge.

778
00:45:05,039 --> 00:45:07,900
[SPEAKER_01] Upravo se o tome razmišljano.

779
00:45:07,900 --> 00:45:10,119
[SPEAKER_01] Što smo rekli u prošloj emisiji,

780
00:45:10,119 --> 00:45:12,639
[SPEAKER_01] nije novac problemi,

781
00:45:12,639 --> 00:45:14,860
[SPEAKER_01] nije novac neko zlo.

782
00:45:14,860 --> 00:45:16,280
[SPEAKER_01] Novac je samo sredstvo.

783
00:45:16,280 --> 00:45:18,519
[SPEAKER_01] Sredstvo kako ćemo mi njega

784
00:45:18,519 --> 00:45:19,940
[SPEAKER_01] upotrijebiti

785
00:45:19,940 --> 00:45:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] ili u kojem smjeru ćemo mi njega

786
00:45:21,800 --> 00:45:22,659
[SPEAKER_01] usmjeriti.

787
00:45:23,159 --> 00:45:25,199
[SPEAKER_01] za što ćemo ga usmjeriti.

788
00:45:25,199 --> 00:45:29,900
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, naravno da mi ekonomisti,

789
00:45:29,900 --> 00:45:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo mi koji se bavimo sa poduzetništvom,

790
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] naravno da se stvara profita.

791
00:45:36,500 --> 00:45:37,739
[SPEAKER_01] Pitanje je, znači,

792
00:45:37,739 --> 00:45:39,559
[SPEAKER_01] kako ćemo mi taj profit

793
00:45:39,559 --> 00:45:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] usmjeriti dalje.

794
00:45:42,699 --> 00:45:44,840
[SPEAKER_01] Da li će to biti, evo,

795
00:45:44,840 --> 00:45:47,440
[SPEAKER_01] za neke želje

796
00:45:47,440 --> 00:45:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] ili će biti za boljitak,

797
00:45:50,119 --> 00:45:51,019
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, društva.

798
00:45:51,019 --> 00:45:52,780
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da mi tu imamo slobodi,

799
00:45:52,780 --> 00:45:54,059
[SPEAKER_01] evo, cijelo vrijeme i o tome

800
00:45:54,059 --> 00:45:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] pričamo, ali

801
00:45:56,119 --> 00:45:57,940
[SPEAKER_01] što je to što će nama doniti

802
00:45:57,940 --> 00:45:59,019
[SPEAKER_01] zadovoljstvo?

803
00:45:59,239 --> 00:46:01,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ne vanjsku neku, eto,

804
00:46:01,460 --> 00:46:02,559
[SPEAKER_01] osmijeh, radost,

805
00:46:02,559 --> 00:46:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] nego unutarnje zadovoljstvo,

806
00:46:04,079 --> 00:46:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] zadovoljstvo koje će biti

807
00:46:05,239 --> 00:46:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] unutar nas, a ne.

808
00:46:06,039 --> 00:46:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] Za to smo mi kršćani,

809
00:46:07,519 --> 00:46:09,219
[SPEAKER_01] to su kršćanske neke vrijednosti.

810
00:46:09,219 --> 00:46:11,619
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno da svako ima slobodu birat

811
00:46:11,619 --> 00:46:15,099
[SPEAKER_01] kako će taj novac svoj potrošiti.

812
00:46:15,099 --> 00:46:16,739
[SPEAKER_01] To je neupitno.

813
00:46:16,739 --> 00:46:18,980
[SPEAKER_01] Stvar je samo da,

814
00:46:18,980 --> 00:46:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] ako smo mi kršćani,

815
00:46:20,539 --> 00:46:23,519
[SPEAKER_01] koje vrijednosti mi

816
00:46:23,519 --> 00:46:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] šaljemo u svijet?

817
00:46:27,980 --> 00:46:30,039
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je to naš način,

818
00:46:30,039 --> 00:46:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] stil života

819
00:46:31,079 --> 00:46:33,199
[SPEAKER_01] koji mi pokazujemo

820
00:46:33,199 --> 00:46:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] drugima?

821
00:46:34,019 --> 00:46:36,679
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, to upravo poslanje

822
00:46:36,679 --> 00:46:39,360
[SPEAKER_01] što smo i danas pričali.

823
00:46:39,360 --> 00:46:42,159
[SPEAKER_01] Koje je to naše ovaj poslanje?

824
00:46:42,159 --> 00:46:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] Da li je naše poslanje,

825
00:46:43,380 --> 00:46:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] znači, da ako imamo novac

826
00:46:45,880 --> 00:46:46,719
[SPEAKER_01] s tim novcem,

827
00:46:46,719 --> 00:46:49,760
[SPEAKER_01] drugoga razveseliti,

828
00:46:49,760 --> 00:46:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] drugome omogućiti

829
00:46:52,119 --> 00:46:53,860
[SPEAKER_01] još bolji neki odnos,

830
00:46:53,860 --> 00:46:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] bolji život?

831
00:46:56,719 --> 00:47:00,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ili nešto drugo.

832
00:47:00,280 --> 00:47:01,840
[SPEAKER_01] Koje je to mjera?

833
00:47:01,840 --> 00:47:03,420
[SPEAKER_01] Koje je to prava mjera?

834
00:47:03,420 --> 00:47:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da nije prava mjera,

835
00:47:05,960 --> 00:47:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] sve dadu drugima.

836
00:47:07,099 --> 00:47:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da to nije prava mjera.

837
00:47:09,239 --> 00:47:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isus je rekao,

838
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] ljubi druge kao što ljubiš sebe.

839
00:47:12,920 --> 00:47:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ljubi Boga iznad svega,

840
00:47:15,320 --> 00:47:17,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali moraš ljubiti sebe,

841
00:47:17,619 --> 00:47:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer i ti si stvorenje Božje.

842
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] I tebe Bog ljubi.

843
00:47:21,780 --> 00:47:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] I Bog želi da se svako od nas ostvari

844
00:47:25,039 --> 00:47:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] i da upunini, upunini.

845
00:47:26,820 --> 00:47:27,820
[SPEAKER_01] I to je Božja volja,

846
00:47:27,820 --> 00:47:28,840
[SPEAKER_01] da budemo sretni,

847
00:47:28,840 --> 00:47:30,739
[SPEAKER_01] da budemo ispunjeni,

848
00:47:30,739 --> 00:47:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] da budemo zadovoljni.

849
00:47:33,380 --> 00:47:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] Marijana,

850
00:47:34,920 --> 00:47:38,219
[SPEAKER_01] evo prošlo je naših sat vremena.

851
00:47:38,219 --> 00:47:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] molim te,

852
00:47:39,079 --> 00:47:41,760
[SPEAKER_01] par rečenica ako želiš za kraj

853
00:47:41,760 --> 00:47:43,360
[SPEAKER_01] reći možda.

854
00:47:43,360 --> 00:47:46,260
[SPEAKER_02] Da, evo,

855
00:47:46,260 --> 00:47:48,599
[SPEAKER_02] kršćanska perspektiva i pogled

856
00:47:48,599 --> 00:47:51,300
[SPEAKER_02] na život ovome svijetu

857
00:47:51,300 --> 00:47:52,960
[SPEAKER_02] je zaista vrlo nadahnjujuća.

858
00:47:52,960 --> 00:47:54,019
[SPEAKER_02] Evo,

859
00:47:54,019 --> 00:47:56,139
[SPEAKER_02] i kaže Papa Franjo

860
00:47:56,139 --> 00:47:58,079
[SPEAKER_02] u Evangeliji Gaudium

861
00:47:58,079 --> 00:47:58,780
[SPEAKER_02] radost evančeva,

862
00:47:58,780 --> 00:48:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] to je naprednje naposloska pobodnica.

863
00:48:00,559 --> 00:48:02,380
[SPEAKER_02] Ko bi mogla zatvoriti

864
00:48:02,380 --> 00:48:03,219
[SPEAKER_02] svetog Franju,

865
00:48:03,219 --> 00:48:04,900
[SPEAKER_02] Asiškoga ili svetu Tereziju

866
00:48:04,900 --> 00:48:05,599
[SPEAKER_02] kao kutu

867
00:48:05,599 --> 00:48:08,119
